<HEADLINE> AP Top News at 1 a.m. EDT  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Friday, Sept. 8, 2000
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Polls: Gore Shows Strength on Issues
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
