By The Associated Press	   Saturday's forecast calls for partly cloudy skies
statewide with
a high in the upper 70s. Saturday night should be mostly clear in
the east with fog developing early Sunday morning. Low in the upper
50s. The western part of the state will be partly cloudy with a low
around 60.
